    "Added a shared import-only script helper for completeness CLI flags, manifest JSON emission, and final threshold decisions.",
    "Wired obs_v2, WU daily, HKO daily, and Ogimet backfills with --completeness-manifest, --expected-count, and --fail-threshold-percent.",
